
PRE-REQUISITES:

Install `ctags` through your package manager.

---

TO INSTALL:

`./configure_vim.sh`

---

VUNDLE (PACKAGE MANAGER):

Vundle will make installing and updating all the other tools much easier. Itâ€™s basically pathogen with a lot of nice extras, like installing the bundles itself from their Github repos (and other sources). For more info see the README in the Github repo.

To install plugins which are at ".vimrc":

    :PluginInstall

    (Alternatively: $ vim +PluginInstall +all)

    After the installation is completed, close the buffer:

        :bdelete

Update the plugins:

    :PluginUpdate
        OR
    :PluginInstall!


See all installed plugins:

    :PluginList


Search for plugins:

    :PluginSearch! [plugin_query]

    Example:
        :PluginSearch! markdown

Delete a plugin:

    Remove it from .vimrc, then:
        (VISUAL) :PluginClean



